&lt;p&gt;On these four runs I had consistent failures with dtests &lt;tt&gt;test_network_topology_strategy&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;test_network_topology_strategy_each_quorum&lt;/tt&gt;. But re-running those tests with xlarge containers fixed it: &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/michaelsembwever/cassandra/69/workflows/470a98f3-c1e4-4a5a-b7e9-cf3dcc807ca5/jobs/3285&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/michaelsembwever/cassandra/69/workflows/470a98f3-c1e4-4a5a-b7e9-cf3dcc807ca5/jobs/3285&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=edimitrova&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;edimitrova&quot;&gt;edimitrova&lt;/a&gt;, i thought we fixed this with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18127&quot; title=&quot;Python upgrade tests can be run successfully with Large instead of XLarge containers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-18127&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-18127&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ?)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;EDIT: nm, i see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18051&quot; title=&quot;Optimize and fix flaky test_network_topology_strategy and test_network_topology_strategy_each_quorum for large containers in CircleCI&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-18051&quot;&gt;CASSANDRA-18051&lt;/a&gt; now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
