&lt;p&gt;Right on spot, I am just looking into this today, the ticket is &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18051&quot; title=&quot;Optimize and fix flaky test_network_topology_strategy and test_network_topology_strategy_each_quorum for large containers in CircleCI&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-18051&quot;&gt;CASSANDRA-18051&lt;/a&gt;. I was just discussing it with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=brandon.williams&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;brandon.williams&quot;&gt;brandon.williams&lt;/a&gt;&#160;in a chat. Those are large tests, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18127&quot; title=&quot;Python upgrade tests can be run successfully with Large instead of XLarge containers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-18127&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-18127&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was about upgrade tests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
